RED FLAG THRESHOLDS (apply conditional formatting):
Conversion_Rate_Pct < 0.5 — RED background
Revenue_USD (daily) < 200 — YELLOW background (day 2 onward only)
Email_Unsubscribes cumulative / total Signups_Kit > 2% — RED background on G column

